err how do i upload quicker to you guys....my first try at uploading.........have it set to no limt upload....is that correct???? help received with thanks.

Nope, not correct. Set it somewhere between 75-80% of your upload bandwidth rate - you need to do this to leave room for acks (IP acknowledgements) to be rec'd from the clients to whom you're uploading.
